## What Gets Filled In on the Form

The following fields are filled in automatically from the CSV:

| Form Column                          | Filled From             |
|--------------------------------------|-------------------------|
| **#**                                | Row number (auto)       |
| **Name (Last, First, MI)**           | LastName, FirstName, MI |
| **Sex (M/F)**                        | Sex                     |
| **Rank/Rate**                        | Rank                    |
| **Age**                              | Age                     |
| **\*Cardio Modality**                | Event                   |
| **PRT Date / Timeslot**(top of form) | Date and Timeslot       |

The following fields are left **blank** for on-site use:

- Number of Push Ups
- Forearm Plank Time
- Cardio Time / Calories
- Member's Signature
- CFL/ACFL Print Name / Signature
- Command UIC

